{"name":"Two-Gun Kid","permission":{"default":0,"89eyOdrISceMvDfi":3},"type":"edge","data":{"description":"<benefit type=”formattedtext”><p>Two-Gun Kid works just like Two-Fisted, but with ranged weapons, allowing her to fire or throw a weapon in each hand as two different actions but without triggering a Multi-Action penalty.</p><p>If the character has Two-Fisted, the second action may also be a melee attack.</p>","notes":"","additionalStats":[],"isArcaneBackground":false,"requirements":{"value":"Novice, Agility d8+"}},"flags":{},"img":"systems/swade/assets/icons/edge.svg","effects":[],"_id":"V4UH5wwAmwEWvd1X"}
